high_descs: Turn left  and go through the kitchen to the front of the counter top on the left of  the sink
Pick up the red tomato on the left side of the counter.
Turn around and go to the front of the refrigerator.
Chill the tomato in the refrigerator and take it out.
Turn around and go left to the front of the microwave above the stove.
Place the chilled tomato in the microwave and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in the microwave

high_descs: Turn left, go forward, turn left and go to the counter
Pick up the tomato on the counter
Turn right, go forward a bit, turn right and go to the fridge
Put the tomato in the fridge, wait, pick up the tomato
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn left and go to the microwave
Put the tomato in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Cool a tomato and put it in the microwave

high_descs: Turn to the left, and then the left again to face the counter.
Pick up the tomato from the left side of the counter.
Carry the tomato and move to the right, then turn around to locate the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the tomato inside. Shut the fridge, then open it. Take the tomato out and shut the door.
Take the tomato and turn around, then left to find the stove. Look up to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the tomato inside.
anns.task_desc: Chill a tomato and place it in the microwave.
